#: page-features.php
msgid "Standings & Tiebreakers"
msgstr "Classifica e spareggi"

#: page-features.php
msgid "Automatic standings with Buchholz, Sonneborn-Berger, rating, and direct encounter tiebreakers."
msgstr "Classifica automatica con spareggi Buchholz, Sonneborn-Berger, rating e scontro diretto."

#: page-features.php
msgid "Printable Pairings"
msgstr "Abbinamenti stampabili"

#: page-features.php
msgid "Generate a round and print the pairing sheet in one click—ready to post on the wall."
